://s2.postimg.org/ezlnk1wk9/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs2.postimg.org%2Fezlnk1wk9%2Fimage.jpg&h=9bd77732&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">相集</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n擺圖用google drive：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/qXk2TG\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FqXk2TG&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6Vv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=6113a2ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/qXk2TG</a><br />\n<br />\nios用Whatsapp save gif 教學：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/EpWsmP\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FEpWsmP&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6Vv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=3b3b9db5\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/EpWsmP</a><br />\n<br />\n華田PS去底小心得：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/YFByBR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FYFByBR&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6Vv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=72217bd6\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/YFByBR</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/BQxA8i5.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FBQxA8i5.gif&h=fd7485c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCredit：華田<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">會員區：</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\nbinc名單：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/Eeyy7O\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FEeyy7O&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6Vv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=d24b2cac\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/Eeyy7O</a><br />\n<br />\n巴打創作：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/mnrGKF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FmnrGKF&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6Vv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=0187a986\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/mnrGKF</a><br />\n<br />\n點名&amp;留言版：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/iiJjsq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FiiJjsq&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6Vv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=5aec8a2f\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/iiJjsq</a>"},{"pid":"f1b2d30f666c5ec2a3b5475fbb078ec47f72b85b","tid":163941,"uid":86378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:44:06.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">新垣結衣x瑛太W主演映畫《ミックス。》(混合雙打)<br />\n挑戰乒乓球題材的浪漫喜劇！ </strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/97B91eP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F97B91eP.jpg&h=61a86686&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4TB523R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4TB523R.jpg&h=c72bb608&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n腳本：古沢良太（Legal High 腳本） <br />\n監督：石川淳一（Legal High 監督） <br />\n<br />\n共演卡司：広末涼子、遠藤憲一、田中美佐子、佐野勇斗、瀬戸康史、永野芽郁、蒼井優、森崎博之、吉田鋼太郎、生瀬勝久、山口紗彌加、斎藤司、久間田琳加、鈴木福、谷花音、真木よう子、小日向文世等。 <br />\n<br />\n　　2月中旬開始攝影，2017年秋全國東寶系公開！ 新垣結衣飾演戀愛和工作都很失敗的原天才乒乓球少女、快30歲的單身OL富田多滿子，與瑛太飾演的原日本職業拳擊手組合成乒乓球混雙，向全國大賽挑戰的故事。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>《Code Blue 3》製作決定!!</strong></span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/10/100302_53bdee902bf86890010775dc3176e6ed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F10%2F100302_53bdee902bf86890010775dc3176e6ed.jpg&h=039dc2f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n5月開拍，時間設定於第2季的七年後，播放時間：7月份 月九<br />\n<br />\n十年過去，各人都走上自己的人生道路。<br />\n藍沢耕作（山下智久）離開咗翔陽大學附屬醫院嘅急症室之後，喺腦外科深造研究，目標係成為最強嘅腦外科醫生。<br />\n白石恵（新垣結衣）就繼續喺人手不足嘅翔北急症室工作，成為咗飛行救護團隊嘅領導醫生奮鬥中！<br />\n緋山美帆子（戸田恵梨香）就去咗備產醫療中心，喺婦產科果度深造。<br />\n冴島はるか（比嘉愛未）依家繼續做緊飛行團隊嘅護士。<br />\n藤川一男（浅利洋介）同白石一齊留咗喺翔北急症室，只係自己向着成為整形外科嘅急症室醫生之路進發。<br />\n面臨新挑戰，失去家人，開始戀愛，在新嘅階段有邊個對手等緊佢哋？<br />\n<br />\n來自 Gakki 的訊息：<br />\n　　「在最初的《Code Blue》拍攝中收到的20歲生日祝福，好像已經過了很久，又像是最近的事。在這20代的最後一年再次扮演白石惠，以及劇組時隔7年的集結，感受到極大的緣分和使命感。全新的《Code Blue》故事中，狀況、立場、所有的事物都有很大的改變，當時一起努力著的5人會有什麼發展我非常期待。希望能讓觀眾看得開心，也希望能夠有所收穫，我會全力以赴的！」<br />\n<a href=\"http://ricgrady.pixnet.net/blog/post/117081740\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fricgrady.pixnet.net%2Fblog%2Fpost%2F117081740&d=cH2nQL%2B7gNVGRZzFZPB6Vv9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=7fd4a3e6\" target=\"_blank\">http://ricgrady.pixnet.net/blog/post/117081740</a>"},{"pid":"467372324a8fdefc664307a7ec260c40a062c73a","tid":163941,"uid":25869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:44:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YBwNE5W.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYBwNE5W.gif&h=ffdacc99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kgF3D5P.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkgF3D5P.gif&h=440eb3de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NrhlD2Q.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNrhlD2Q.gif&h=d9d5a7a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6016NH8.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6016NH8.gif&h=9443f24d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://s3.postimg.org/y58xdzrgj/9de00018ff437fcb06c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs3.postimg.org%2Fy58xdzrgj%2F9de00018ff437fcb06c.gif&h=6a97fa4a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8s25288.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8s25288.jpg&h=c4e7c9d2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cVLrJu1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcVLrJu1.jpg&h=e581a5d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n留名（第一頁）<br />\n唔理咁多，留咗名先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5c8c672534eebb350a76b74e85a42710c8d1dd6","tid":163941,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-20T10:44:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/s1O6D1b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fs1